Definition: something that causes or entails suffering
Example: I cannot think it a hardship that more indulgence is allowed to men than to women- James Boswell; the many hardships of frontier life
Synonyms: misfortune, something, that, causes, or, entails, suffering, I, cannot, think, it, a, more, indulgence, is, allowed, to, men, than, women, -, James, Boswell, the, many, hardships, of, frontier, life
Category: noun.event
